data.description: Property qualifies for ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE with interest rate way below market value. 3.5 interest rate available upon approval! This 2bd/2.5ba Near Northside townhouse offers urban elegance at its finest! The 1st floor features a flex space perfect for an office or den. On the 2nd level, you'll love the open feeling of the living room, gourmet kitchen, & dining room. Don't forget the new electric fireplace, providing coziness & ambiance. The kitchen boasts 42" upper cabinets, upgraded tile, & stainless steel appliances. On the 3rd level, you'll find two spacious bedrooms with en-suite bathrooms & walk-in closets - the primary includes a balcony! Full of Onyx & East upgrades & features newly added LVP throughout the home. Easy access to downtown Indy's shopping & entertainment!
